<H2><B><EM>
  <FONT color="FF0000">
    Reasons to Choose PowerSubmit
  </FONT>
</EM></B></H2>
</CENTER>
 
<HR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=+1><EM>
 
<P>
<FONT COLOR="0000FF">
<UL>
  <LI><B>You complete only one form</B><BR>
      This automatically fills out the rest of
      the submission requirements for search engines' registration.  This
      eliminates input error and guarantees more efficient submission process.
      Once the form is completed all you have to do is click with the mouse.
      <BR><BR>

  <LI>Receive instant feedback when submission is completed.
      <BR><BR>

  <LI>Enables you to conduct and update your own website promotion
      <BR><BR>

  <LI>We maintain and update our information on search engines making our
      list valid and current
      <BR><BR>

  <LI>We offer submission to over 500 search engines, directories, indexes,
      free for all lists
      <BR><BR>

  <LI><B>Unlimited access</B> for submission
      <BR><BR>

  <LI>Unlike others, we offer a <B>free</B> demo of our services
      for you to try out and see for yourself
      <BR><BR>

  <LI>The <B>BEST</B> value for your money
