<DOCHDR>
http://carnetwork.com:80/racernet/tech.html 207.158.244.233 19970115170351 text/html 6100
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 17:03:49 GMT
Server: Apache/1.2b4
Connection: close
