  THE LATEST DEVELOPMENTS</b><br>
     How will your company implement effective strategies to  cope with the new            developments affecting taxation and royalties for t he mining industry in Southeas Asian                                                                                    countries?  This session will update you on the latest changes in mining laws and taxes - comparing and contrasting countries with an emphasis on countries that have made changes in the last year.  Examine the implications of foreign taxes on your daily business
  decisions and discover how competitive Southeast Asian taxation schemes are             from a global
  perspective.<br>
