<h1><a name="top"></a>GOOD PRACTICE
<P></h1>
<h2>Signs of quality in<br>
Upper-Secondary Schools</h2></B> <P>
<P>
<P>

<P>
<P>
<i>Department of <br>
Upper-Secondary Education<br>
Ministry of Education<br>
Denmark<P></i>
<P><a href="practcov.htm"><i>See cover</i></a>
<P>
