<P><IMG SRC="ball.gif">  <A HREF="special.htm">Special Reports:  The
Privatization of Brazil's Electricity Sector.</A></P>
<P><IMG SRC="ball.gif">  <A HREF="confo.htm">Conference Information</A></P>
<P><IMG SRC="ball.gif">  Find out about <A HREF="order.htm">subscription
rates</A> for L.A.I.S. publications.</P>
