on the Sept 6 and 7th MIS&T meeting on Encryption Export/Key Escrow.
The URL: is <A HREF="http://www.isse.gmu.edu/~pfarrell/nistmeeting.html">http://www.isse.gmu.edu/~pfarrell/nistmeeting.html</A> <P>

On it are all the official Government handouts, copies of all the
slides and presentations that are public and on the net, and
my "official" report on the two breaksessions that I was the
"official" recorder. <P>

Pat <P>

