<title>Daily Chat on CIS899: IP: Java Cup International -- $1,000,000 in prizes</title>
<h1>IP: Java Cup International -- $1,000,000 in prizes</h1>
Dave Farber (<i>farber@central.cis.upenn.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Sun, 03 Dec 1995 22:20:08 -0500</i>
