<i>&gt; Digicash started an E-cash trial in October 1994, which is still not over yet. According to the</i><br>
<p>
	i think it is over.<br>
	they stop accepting new registrations.<br>
<p>
from <a href="http://www.digicash.com/ecash/trial.html">http://www.digicash.com/ecash/trial.html</a> ...<br>
<p>
The ecash trial started in October 1994. Today, one year later, we are pleased to say that it has been<br>
a great succes. Well over ten thousand people have registered, and we have issued one million<br>
cyberbucks. We now stop accepting new registrations, but will continue to run the trial and support<br>
everyone who registered. <br>
<p>
