Hygon Kim is defending his thesis at 1 pm on Thursday. It was the only time<br>
that was available for the next weeks for several of the committ members. I<br>
am Kims thesis supervisor and thus need to be there. It would  have been  a<br>
real hardship on Kim to postphone possibly till after xmas. I would like to<br>
canel Thursday class and MAKE IT up with an extended class sometime soon<br>
when we have a visitor.<br>
<p>
I hope you understand and agree with me<br>
<p>
Dave<br>
