<title>Daily Chat on CIS899: Re: Penn In-touch</title>
<h1>Re: Penn In-touch</h1>
Jeffrey D. Chung (<i>jdchung@viper.cis.upenn.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 17 Oct 1995 10:58:29 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#97">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#97">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#97">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#97">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
