 &lt; is edited by J. Crowcroft, D. Estrin, H. Schulzrinne,<br>
 &lt; and M. Schwartz.<br>
 &lt;<br>
 &lt; The online version of IEEE JSAC is currently available<br>
 &lt; free of charge.  However, you will need to register to<br>
 &lt; view the full text of articles.  Those who registered<br>
 &lt; prior to October 1 will need to register again.<br>
