<TITLE>Readings distributed by Professor Farber</TITLE>
<H1>Readings distributed by Professor Farber</H1>

The primary links go to the txt file.  I ran all the txt files
through a txt2html filter, and the unattended results are available in
the (hypertext) links.  If the hypertext looks wonky, you're advised
to go back to txt.  These files are available in the directory
<CODE>/mnt/eniac/home1/m/mengwong/html/cis590/</CODE> as
<CODE>reading.*.txt</CODE> for your convenience. <P>

